title: 156: Has Music Become Too Disposable? | Ear Biscuits Ep. 156
description:
Rhett and Link look back on the origin of their love of analog music, how streaming services have changed their listening habits, and Link's experience as a fly on the wall as his cousin recorded his album on this week's episode of Ear Biscuits.
